Description:
This is the sniffer application that collects visible mac-addresses and
sends them to the backend for data processing.

How to use:
1. Install golang and tshark (apt-get, pacman, etc)
2. $ source setup-env.sh
   (Let's fetch the dependencies)
3. $ go get github.com/golang/glog         Logging tool
4. $ go get github.com/ogier/pflag          POSIX style flags
6. Edit the code (optional)
7. $ cd src/hubben.chalmers.it/wiith/
8. $ go install
9. $ wiith --help
10. $ screen -S wiith -U wiith
11. ...
12. PROFIT

